Yaar nu milegi aaj laash yaar di.. 
(*everything starts to dwell into a silent hollowness.*)
And in that moment, something breaks inside. :)

Yes, we are humans. :) Love makes us live, separation kills.

May everyone who loves truly get a chance to live a lifetime on this Earth. Eternity is awesome but surviving as humans is just another kind of heaven and every couple deserves to experience. :)

Villains of love must retire.
